The Munchkin Soft Tip Infant Spoons are ideal for your little one and make for a great feeding accessory.

The ergonomically designed spoon handles give you easy grip and they are long enough to help you get to the bottom of the baby food jars. Munchkin Soap Dispensing Bottle Brush (Blue) Price: Rs.473

Maintaining a certain level of hygiene for babies and their accessories is of vital importance to ensure their healthy growth and development. The bottles used for feeding the baby need to be kept clean and sterilized to avoid contamination due to harmful bacteria and fungi.

The Bottle Brush from Munchkin is designed in a customized manner to enable you to clean the bottles thoroughly. Its Soap Dispensing Feature allows you to dispense the right amount of soap in the bottle at the touch of a button and clean it even in the innermost areas. The cleaning material is made out of Nylon but ensures that it does not scratch the bottle in any way. The Grip of this Bottle Brush is a Non-Slip Grip for easy and comfortable cleaning. This Munchkin Soap Dispensing Bottle Brush is Top Rack Dishwasher Safe
column15:
making it convenient and easy to use.

\n
